    "description": "Join the 1mg Capital India family as a Full Stack Developer in Allahabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout 1mg Capital India:\n1mg Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 1mg Capital India!",
